<br>
These are his words from a single recent post string, referring to a system of reservations and those who support it:<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;It restricts legitimate hard working guild raids because some penny ante posse wants phat lootzor.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;I'm getting pretty sick of seeing the entitlement whores moan, bitch and whine.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;Do some pheakin interaction in game and make alot of friends, or get get with someone who does.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;There is no difference between 'uber' people and 'non-uber' people' except laziness versus dedication. If you are dedicated you get rewarded. If you are lazy you get what you get.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;Yes, you have calmly and nicely conveyed my vision of an entitlement whore.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;Ignorance is bliss. well you have to grow up some day.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;And back to the point of the thread, you're an absolute git to have issues with people killing wtf, when the heck ever they choose unless YOU'RE THERE with a FORCE ABLE TO KILL IT. Yeah! That makes you get off your lazy, anti-social hineys, make friends, kiss some ass, do what you gotta do to get what you want...&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;Before I got my first character to 50, the servers I often played on had scheduling for planes, fire giants, naggy and vox. I thought this was great because I was a casual player at least half of the year, and I couldn't gavy the people who opposed it... because I was conditioned, pampered and blind. I was turned on by the notion that I didn't really have to work hard at achieving what was , in those times, the 'end game scenarios'. The spirit of accomplishment and acquisition by earning was lost on me.&quot;<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;If you pull your heads from your asses and do a little homework you might realize that my opinions are in the best interest of a server on which you've chosen to grow up.&quot;<br>
<br>
I mention this because I just happen to be one of the people who disagree with Heagan about the issue, which I guess makes me, to summarize, a &quot;penny ante posse-entitlement whore who moans, bitches, and whines, has no friends, and is a lazy, ignorant, blind, pampered, conditioned git, with my head up my ass, and who the spirit of accomplishment and acquisition by learning is lost upon.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yup. I can see why some people react to him the way they do.<br>
